' Shared render profile for print/PPT legibility
' Keep diagrams readable when exported to PNG/SVG and printed on Letter paper.

skinparam dpi 180
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam Padding 8
skinparam nodesep 28
skinparam ranksep 32

' Constrain overall size so diagrams are easier to place on Letter or slides.
scale max 1200 width
